      "message": "*userOptions\n?\notherwise the struct is copied to do the check\n\nor, a slightly cleaner API might be to add a type for format\n\n  type format string\n\nand `func (f format) isHTML() bool`\n\nthen you don\u0027t have to document \"valid formats\" in L168 or L181 because the type would be `format`",
